        },
        "faq_4": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How does HydroLid support hydration needs during firefighting operations?",
            "answer": "HydroLid provides firefighters with quick and hands-free hydration access, allowing them to stay focused on the task without having to stop to access their insulated bottles. With temperature-stable hydration, products like the HydroLid Base Kit and HydroLid Field and Fire Kit ensure that firefighters remain refreshed, enhancing stamina and efficiency during firefighting operations."
          }
        },
        "faq_5": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is HydroLid compatible with the gear typically used by fire departments?",
            "answer": "Yes, HydroLid is designed with versatility in mind and can be used with wide-mouth bottles such as Hydro Flask, ThermoFlask and CamelBak insulated bottles. The lightweight and functional design allows it to integrate seamlessly with standard firefighting equipment."
